rms.model

Class ResourceType

  • java.lang.Object
    • rms.model.ResourceType

  • public class ResourceType
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is meant to be used with the PRMS database. It is a model class for the ResourceType table in the database. Each type of resource is given a unique ID. Each ID represents a resource type with name, description, and an image path.
